//////////////////////
TO START:
At first you need to run "npm install" and then "npm start" in frontend directory, to start the frontend. Second of all you need to run "python manage.py runserver" in backend directory to start the backend.
//////////////////////


when you testing api and the response in huge html with no sense

try to make CORS_ALLOW_ALL_ORIGINS
and
debug = false
and
add to allowed hosts your local, if not yet

in settings

(restore them back after you finished)


